Boiler Node
===========

This is a boilerplate for a node.js application using the MVC file structure.

Mocha
Jade
Stylus
Hiredis
Socket io
Redis
Node-dev

\--app (Node Server Javascript)
|  \--controllers
|  \--models
|  \--views
|  \--helpers.coffee
|  \--socket-io.coffee
|
\--assets (Client-side pre-compilation assets)
|  \--scripts (Client-side coffeescript)
|  |  \--vendor (bower directory. .bowerrc = "directory": "assets/scripts/vendor")
|  |  \--coffeescript
|  |     \--grunt.coffee
|  \--stylesheets (SASS, STYLUS, LESS stylesheets)
|
\--dist (Minified files for distribution)
|  \--stylesheets
|  \--javascripts
|  \--images
|
\--bin (Scripts to run)
|  \--devserver
|  \--test
|  \--watch
|
\--src (Server-side pre-compilation assets)
|  \--build
|     \--app.build.js
|     \--build.sh*
|
\--public
|  \--stylesheets
|  \--javascripts
|  \--images
|
\--test
|  \--apps
|  \--models
|  \--_helper.js
|
\--app.js
\--package.json
\--grunt.js
